code: @Override public boolean isNestedArchive(Archive.Entry entry) {     if (entry.isDirectory()) {         return entry.getName().equals(WEB_INF_CLASSES).     } else {         return entry.getName().startsWith(WEB_INF_LIB) || entry.getName().startsWith(WEB_INF_LIB_PROVIDED).     } }
public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {     new WarLauncher().launch(args). }
